X = X_1 + ... + X_{10}
 \begin{align} X_i = \begin{cases} 1 &\mbox{if } \text{object i is chosen by A and B} \\ 0 &\mbox{otherwise } \end{cases}  \end{align} 
 E[X_i] = 0\cdot P(X_i = 0) + 1\cdot P(X_i = 1) = P(X_i = 1) = 9/100. 
E[X] = 10\cdot E[X_i] = 0.9
